entries.femaleVariant: And then the Black Wraith saw a bright, greenish flash on the horizon.
Oh, please. Things like that don't happen in real life.
His betrayal was forgotten. He saw he had been given a second chance.
The figure reached out to him... And boom! The Black Wraith woke up, back in camp with his family.
Now, he thought it was an AV that crashed... But as he drew closer, he saw a mysterious figure, floating just above the ground.
